            </p>
        </div>
        <div class = 'carousel-item text-center'>
            <p class = 'storyBook'>
                The electromagnetic waves landed all over the earth.
                Some of them landed on the leaves of an apple tree.
                Inside those leaves, the plant cells used the light to turn
                carbon dioxide from the air into sugars molecules of an apple.
                This process was called photosynthesis.
            </p>
